### 5. Relation Methods

#### Eager Loading (on query builder)

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `.select_<rel>()` | Eagerly load the related entity/entities |
| `.with_<rel>_matching(sub)` | Filter parent rows by a condition on the relation |

#### Parent (forward FK) — on entity instance

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `.r()` | Access the loaded parent entity |
| `.r_id()` | Get the foreign key value |
| `.update_r_id(id)` | Change the foreign key (tracked) |

#### Children (reverse FK) — on entity instance

| Method | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `.r_list()` | Immutable slice of loaded children |
| `.r_list_mut()` | Mutable access to loaded children |

