### 6. Status Enum Shortcuts

When an entity has a `status` field backed by an enum, convenience methods are
generated for each enum code:

**On the query builder:**

```rust
Q::orders()
    .with_status_is_pending()         // filter: status == PENDING
    .with_status_is_not_cancelled()   // filter: status != CANCELLED
```

**On the entity instance:**

```rust
order.update_status_to_shipped();     // set status = SHIPPED
if order.status_is_delivered() {      // check status == DELIVERED
    // ...
}
```

