### 7. Mutation Patterns

#### Create

```rust
let mut new_entity = Entity::new();
new_entity.update_field_a("value");
new_entity.update_field_b(42);
new_entity
    .save(&ctx)
    .comment("Create a new entity")
    .purpose("Needed for ...")
    .await?;
```

#### Update

```rust
let mut entity = Q::entities()
    .with_id_is(target_id)
    .comment("Load entity for update")
    .purpose("Update field_a value")
    .execute_for_first(&ctx).await?
    .ok_or_else(|| anyhow!("not found"))?;

entity.update_field_a("new value");
entity
    .save(&ctx)
    .comment("Update entity field_a")
    .purpose("Reflect new business state")
    .await?;
```

#### Delete

```rust
entity
    .delete(&ctx)
    .comment("Remove entity")
    .purpose("Clean up after process completion")
    .await?;
```

